We may from time to time disclose the personal information that we receive from you to certain selected organisations, sub-contractors and agents to whom we outsource certain functions for example, mailing houses, persons answering customer support inquiries or performing statistical analysis of our services and products, including such organisations, sub-contractors and agents that are located outside Australia. We may from time to time disclose the personal information that we receive from you to other related bodies corporate of Toby’s Estate, including those that are located outside Australia.
We will not pass on your information for direct marketing purposes to anyone other than the persons or organisations set out above unless you have indicated to us that you would like to receive information about products and services.
Why we collect your personal information?
We may collect your personal information, including sensitive information, for a number of reasons, including:
(a) suggesting and selecting products which may interest you;
(b) providing general health information, and information on products and services;
(c) customising of certain products and/or services;
(d) conducting analysis for marketing and research so that we can improve our products;
(e) conducting statistical analysis, in order that we can better understand your needs and/or discern general patterns and trends of consumption;
(f) to conduct and administer competitions and promotions;
(g) sending you publications, correspondences, email releases, updates or notifications;
(h) providing access to restricted areas of the Site; and
(i) for such other purposes as you have previously agreed to.
From time to time, we may have contests or competitions and you will have to supply us with specific personally identifying information. In such cases please note that the Privacy Policy may be varied and the changes brought to your attention in the relevant pages of the Site.
The above shall not apply or shall cease to apply to such information as (a) has become public knowledge other than through disclosure by Toby’s Estate, (b) was already known to Toby’s Estate prior to your disclosure, or (c) is required to be disclosed by Toby’s Estate by any competent judicial, governmental or regulatory body; laws or regulations of Australia or any other territory.
